<!DOCTYPE html><html class="client-nojs" lang="ru" dir="ltr"> <body> <h2><span class="mw-headline" id=".D0.9F.D1.80.D0.B0.D0.B7.D0.B4.D0.BD.D0.B8.D0.BA.D0.B8">Праздники</span> </span></h2> <h3><span class="mw-headline" id=".D0.9D.D0.B0.D1.86.D0.B8.D0.BE.D0.BD.D0.B0.D0.BB.D1.8C.D0.BD.D1.8B.D0.B5">Национальные</span> </span></h3><ul><li><span class="nowrap"><span style="display: none; speak: none;" class="noprint">Бразилия</span><span style="white-space:nowrap;"><span class="flagicon"><a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%91%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B7%D0%B8%D0%BB%D0%B8%D1%8F" title="Бразилия"><img alt="Flag of Brazil.svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/05/Flag_of_Brazil.svg/22px-Flag_of_Brazil.svg.png" width="22" height="15" class="thumbborder" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/05/Flag_of_Brazil.svg/33px-Flag_of_Brazil.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/05/Flag_of_Brazil.svg/44px-Flag_of_Brazil.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="720" data-file-height="504" /></a></span>&#160;<a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%91%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B7%D0%B8%D0%BB%D0%B8%D1%8F" title="Бразилия"><span style="white-space: normal;">Бразилия</span></a></span></span>:<ul><li>Начинается неделя памяти <a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A0%D0%B5%D0%B2%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%8E%D1%86%D0%B8%D1%8F_%D0%A4%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%BF%D0%B8%D0%BB%D1%8C%D1%8F" class="mw-redirect" title="Революция Фарропилья">Революции Фарропилья</a> .</li><li><a href="https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dia_da_cacha%C3%A7a" class="extiw" title="pt:Dia da cachaça">Национальный день</a><span class="noprint" style="font-size:95%; position: relative; top: .4em;">&#160;<span class="ref-info" title="на португальском языке">(порт.)</span></span><span class="link-ru metadata noprint" style="font-size:80%; margin-left:-1.7em; position: relative; top: -.4em;"><a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%D0%9D%D0%B0%D1%86%D0%B8%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%B0%D0%BB%D1%8C%D